<ul>
<li> 
    Usage of small "chemical_input_applet" inputfield :
    <ul>
	<li>
	    Mouseclick on small "greenish" area activates the input
	</li>
	<li>
	    Mouseclick marks character [color red]
	</li>
	<li>
	    "Enter" or "escape" unmarks character; next input at the end
	</li>
	<li>
	    Arrow key used for up/down , left right
	</li>
	<li>
	    Backspace and Delete delete marked [red] character ; or if unmarked , deletes chars from right to left
	</li>
	<li>
	    <ul>
		<li>F1 increase fontsize</li>
		<li>F2 decrease fontsize</li>
		<li>F3 insert Rightarrow</li>
		<li>F4 Insert LeftRightarrow</li>
		<li>F5 change pencolor</li>
		<li>F6 change color background 1 </li>
		<li>F7 change color background 2 </li>
		<li>F8 delete all user inputtext<br />
		In case of preview exercise text, this will be restored</li>
		<li> "->" will append Rightarrow</li>
	    </ul>
	</li>
    </ul>
</li>
	
